msgid "# DeepSeek-V4-Pro"
msgstr "# DeepSeek-V4-Pro"

msgid "## 1 Introduction"
msgstr "## 1 引言"

msgid "DeepSeek-V4 introduces several key upgrades over DeepSeek-V3:"
msgstr "DeepSeek-V4 在 DeepSeek-V3 的基础上引入了多项关键升级："

msgid ""
"- The Manifold-Constrained Hyper-Connections (mHC) to strengthen conventional residual connections.\n"
"- A hybrid attention architecture, which greatly improves long-context efficiency through Compress-4-Attention and Compress-128-Attention. For the Mixture-of-Experts (MoE) components, it still adopts the DeepSeekMoE architecture, with only minor adjustments."
msgstr ""
"- 流形约束超连接（mHC），用于增强传统的残差连接。\n"
"- 混合注意力架构，通过 Compress-4-Attention 和 Compress-128-Attention 大幅提升长上下文效率。对于混合专家（MoE）组件，仍采用 DeepSeekMoE 架构，仅做了细微调整。"

msgid ""
"DeepSeek-V4-Pro, the maximum reasoning effort mode of DeepSeek-V4, "
"significantly advances the knowledge capabilities of open-source models, "
"firmly establishing itself as the best open-source model available today. It"
" achieves top-tier performance in coding benchmarks and significantly "
"bridges the gap with leading closed-source models on reasoning and agentic "
"tasks."
msgstr ""
"DeepSeek-V4-Pro 是 DeepSeek-V4 "
"的最大推理努力模式，显著提升了开源模型的知识能力，牢固确立了其作为当前最佳开源模型的地位。它在编程基准测试中取得了顶级性能，并在推理和智能体任务上显著缩小了与领先闭源模型的差距。"

msgid ""
"This document will show the main verification steps of the model, including "
"supported features, feature configuration, environment preparation, single-"
"node and multi-node deployment, accuracy and performance evaluation."
msgstr "本文档将展示该模型的主要验证步骤，包括支持的特性、特性配置、环境准备、单节点和多节点部署、精度及性能评估。"

msgid ""
"> **Note**: Please replace the version placeholder above with your actual "
"validation version."
msgstr "> **注意**：请将上述版本占位符替换为您实际的验证版本。"

msgid "## 2 Supported Features"
msgstr "## 2 支持的特性"

msgid ""
"Refer to [supported "
"features](../../user_guide/support_matrix/supported_models.md) to get the "
"model's supported feature matrix."
msgstr ""
"请参考[支持的特性](../../user_guide/support_matrix/supported_models.md)获取该模型的支持特性矩阵。"

msgid ""
"Refer to [feature guide](../../user_guide/feature_guide/index.md) to get the"
" feature's configuration."
msgstr "请参考[特性指南](../../user_guide/feature_guide/index.md)获取特性的配置方法。"

msgid "## 3 Prerequisites"
msgstr "## 3 前提条件"

msgid "### 3.1 Model Weight"
msgstr "### 3.1 模型权重"

msgid ""
"- `DeepSeek-V4-Pro-w4a8-mtp` (Quantized version): requires 2 Atlas 800 A3 "
"(128G × 8) nodes or 4 Atlas 800 A2 (64G × 8) nodes. [Download model "
"weight](https://www.modelscope.cn/models/Eco-Tech/DeepSeek-V4-Pro-w4a8-mtp)"
msgstr ""
"- `DeepSeek-V4-Pro-w4a8-mtp`（量化版本）：需要 2 个 Atlas 800 A3（128G × 8）节点或 4 个 "
"Atlas 800 A2（64G × 8）节点。[下载模型权重](https://www.modelscope.cn/models/Eco-"
"Tech/DeepSeek-V4-Pro-w4a8-mtp)"

msgid ""
"It is recommended to download the model weight to the shared directory of "
"multiple nodes, such as `/root/.cache/`."
msgstr "建议将模型权重下载到多节点的共享目录中，例如 `/root/.cache/`。"

msgid "### 3.2 Verify Multi-node Communication (Optional)"
msgstr "### 3.2 验证多节点通信（可选）"

msgid ""
"If you want to deploy a multi-node environment, you need to verify multi-"
"node communication according to [verify multi-node communication "
"environment](../../installation.md#verify-multi-node-communication)."
msgstr ""
"如果您想部署多节点环境，需要按照[验证多节点通信环境](../../installation.md#verify-multi-node-"
"communication)中的说明验证多节点通信。"

msgid "## 4 Installation"
msgstr "## 4 安装"

msgid "### 4.1 Docker Image Installation"
msgstr "### 4.1 Docker 镜像安装"

msgid ""
"Select an image based on your machine type and start the docker image on "
"your node, refer to [using docker](../../installation.md#set-up-using-"
"docker)."
msgstr ""
"根据您的机器类型选择镜像，并在节点上启动 docker 镜像，请参考[使用 docker](../../installation.md#set-up-"
"using-docker)。"

msgid "Start the docker image on each node."
msgstr "在每个节点上启动 docker 镜像。"

msgid ""
"After a successful docker run, you can verify the running container service "
