msgid "## 5 Online Service Deployment"
msgstr "## 5 在线服务部署"

msgid ""
"In this tutorial, we suppose you downloaded the model weight to "
"`/root/.cache/modelscope/hub/models/vllm-ascend/`. Feel free to change it to"
" your own path."
msgstr ""
"在本教程中，我们假设您已将模型权重下载到 `/root/.cache/modelscope/hub/models/vllm-"
"ascend/`。您可以根据需要将其更改为自己的路径。"

msgid ""
"It is recommended that the following service code be encapsulated in a .sh "
"script file and executed in Bash mode."
msgstr "建议将以下服务代码封装在 .sh 脚本文件中，并以 Bash 模式执行。"

msgid "### 5.1 Multi-Node Online Deployment"
msgstr "### 5.1 多节点在线部署"

msgid ""
"The quantized model `DeepSeek-V4-Pro-w4a8-mtp` requires at least 2 Atlas 800"
" A3 (128G × 8) nodes or 4 Atlas 800 A2 (64G × 8) nodes. Run the following "
"scripts on each node respectively."
msgstr ""
"量化模型 `DeepSeek-V4-Pro-w4a8-mtp` 至少需要 2 个 Atlas 800 A3（128G × 8）节点或 4 个 Atlas"
" 800 A2（64G × 8）节点。请分别在每个节点上运行以下脚本。"

msgid "=== \"A2 series\""
msgstr "=== \"A2 系列\""

msgid "**Node1-Node3**"
msgstr "**节点1-节点3**"

msgid "=== \"A3 series\""
msgstr "=== \"A3 系列\""

msgid "**Node0**"
msgstr "**节点0**"

msgid "**Node1**"
msgstr "**节点1**"

msgid ""
"- `--data-parallel-start-rank` specifies the starting data parallel rank of the current node. Each node must be set to a unique value (e.g., Node0 = 0, Node1 = 1).\n"
"- `--data-parallel-address` specifies the IP address of the data parallel master node (Node0). It must be consistent across all nodes.\n"
"- `--headless` (used on non-master nodes) disables the API server on the node, since only the master node serves requests.\n"
"- `--max-model-len` specifies the maximum context length. Adjust it according to your actual scenario.\n"
"- `--speculative-config` configures the MTP (Multi-Token Prediction) speculative decoding to accelerate inference.\n"
"- `--compilation-config '{\"cudagraph_mode\":\"FULL_DECODE_ONLY\"}'` enables full ACL graph execution in the decode phase to reduce scheduling latency.\n"
"- `--async-scheduling` enables asynchronous scheduling to overlap CPU scheduling with NPU computation.\n"
"- `VLLM_ASCEND_ENABLE_FLASHCOMM1=1` enables the FlashComm communication optimization."
msgstr ""
"- `--data-parallel-start-rank` 指定当前节点的数据并行起始 rank。每个节点必须设置为唯一值（例如，节点0 = 0，节点1 = 1）。\n"
"- `--data-parallel-address` 指定数据并行主节点（节点0）的 IP 地址。所有节点必须保持一致。\n"
"- `--headless`（在非主节点上使用）禁用该节点上的 API 服务器，因为只有主节点处理请求。\n"
"- `--max-model-len` 指定最大上下文长度。请根据实际场景进行调整。\n"
"- `--speculative-config` 配置 MTP（多 Token 预测）推测解码以加速推理。\n"
"- `--compilation-config '{\"cudagraph_mode\":\"FULL_DECODE_ONLY\"}'` 在解码阶段启用完整的 ACL 图执行，以减少调度延迟。\n"
"- `--async-scheduling` 启用异步调度，使 CPU 调度与 NPU 计算重叠。\n"
"- `VLLM_ASCEND_ENABLE_FLASHCOMM1=1` 启用 FlashComm 通信优化。"

msgid ""
