msgid "Service Verification:"
msgstr "服务验证："

msgid "### 5.2 Multi-Node PD Separation Deployment"
msgstr "### 5.2 多节点 PD 分离部署"

msgid ""
"We recommend using Mooncake for deployment: "
"[Mooncake](../features/pd_disaggregation_mooncake_multi_node.md)."
msgstr ""
"我们推荐使用 Mooncake "
"进行部署：[Mooncake](../features/pd_disaggregation_mooncake_multi_node.md)。"

msgid ""
"In the standard deployment mode, Prefill (prompt processing) and Decode "
"(token generation) tasks run on the same set of NPUs. PD (Prefill-Decode) "
"separation addresses this by running Prefill and Decode on dedicated node "
"groups, each configured independently. This architecture is recommended for "
"production deployments with concurrent multi-user workloads, where stable "
"latency and high throughput are both required."
msgstr ""
"在标准部署模式下，Prefill（提示处理）和Decode（令牌生成）任务在同一组NPU上运行。PD（Prefill-"
"Decode）分离通过将Prefill和Decode运行在专用节点组上（每组独立配置）来解决此问题。对于需要同时保证稳定延迟和高吞吐量的并发多用户工作负载的生产部署，建议采用此架构。"

msgid ""
"The following sections describe PD separation deployment on both Atlas 800 "
"A3 (128G × 8) and Atlas 800 A2 (64G × 8) multi-node environments."
msgstr "以下章节描述了在Atlas 800 A3（128G × 8）和Atlas 800 A2（64G × 8）多节点环境下的PD分离部署。"

msgid "#### 5.2.1 A3 Series PD Separation Deployment"
msgstr "#### 5.2.1 A3系列PD分离部署"

msgid ""
"This section shows the deployment guide of DeepSeek-V4-Pro on Atlas 800 A3 "
"(128G × 8) multi-node environment with 1P1D for better performance."
msgstr ""
"本节展示了在Atlas 800 A3（128G × 8）多节点环境下，以1P1D配置部署DeepSeek-V4-Pro以获得更优性能的指南。"

msgid "Parameter descriptions:"
msgstr "参数说明："

msgid ""
"|Parameter|Type|Required|Default|Description|\n"
"    |---------|----|--------|-------|-----------|\n"
"    |`--dp-size`|int|Yes|-|Data parallel size (total number of DP ranks across all nodes).|\n"
"    |`--tp-size`|int|No|1|Tensor parallel size within each DP rank.|\n"
"    |`--dp-size-local`|int|No|(same as `--dp-size`)|Number of DP ranks on the current node. If not set, defaults to `--dp-size`.|\n"
"    |`--dp-rank-start`|int|No|0|Starting rank offset for data parallel ranks on this node.|\n"
"    |`--dp-address`|str|Yes|-|IP address of the data parallel master node.|\n"
"    |`--dp-rpc-port`|str|No|12345|RPC port for data parallel master communication.|\n"
"    |`--vllm-start-port`|int|No|9000|Starting port for each vLLM engine instance on this node.|"
msgstr ""
"|参数|类型|必填|默认值|描述|\n"
"    |---------|----|--------|-------|-----------|\n"
"    |`--dp-size`|int|是|-|数据并行大小（所有节点上的DP rank总数）。|\n"
"    |`--tp-size`|int|否|1|每个DP rank内的张量并行大小。|\n"
"    |`--dp-size-local`|int|否|(与`--dp-size`相同)|当前节点上的DP rank数量。如果未设置，默认为`--dp-size`。|\n"
"    |`--dp-rank-start`|int|否|0|此节点上数据并行rank的起始偏移量。|\n"
"    |`--dp-address`|str|是|-|数据并行主节点的IP地址。|\n"
"    |`--dp-rpc-port`|str|否|12345|数据并行主节点通信的RPC端口。|\n"
"    |`--vllm-start-port`|int|否|9000|此节点上每个vLLM引擎实例的起始端口。|"

msgid "3. Decode node (Same as another D node)"
msgstr "3. Decode节点（与另一个D节点相同）"

msgid "3. Decode node 0"
msgstr "3. Decode节点0"

